section.section:
Subject to the requirements of subsections (e) through (m) of this section, a licensee may hold any combination of the following licenses:
One 1-year license under subsection (e) of this section;
One 5-year license under subsection (m) of this section;
One enterprise zone license in each of two enterprise zones under subsection (f) of this section;
One Rockville license under subsection (g) of this section;
One Germantown license under subsection (h) of this section;
One Gaithersburg license under subsection (i) of this section;
One Montgomery Village license under subsection (j) of this section;
One East County license under subsection (k) of this section; and
Two incentive licenses under subsection (l) of this section.
